{
  "stem": "9728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this nobody, nobody in the whole wide world knows about this except people who worked in the cemetery during the year '42 and '43.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were called to leave the cemetery right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not know this in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were told to leave right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all had to leave-- every single worker-- except the people who were in charge of the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were two people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Steinberg, and the other one was [GERMAN] Now, [GERMAN] was in charge of the cemetery from even before the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, as I mentioned, there were two families that they lived on the cemetery grounds.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- building where they lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before the war, this was their residence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, everyone else had to leave the cemetery except those in charge, and those people that lived there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was probably about six, seven times during mine work on the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened is this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came up about seven, eight cars with Germans-- German soldiers, SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "High-ranking soldiers and civilians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the cars were packed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "According what I found out is that they told those people that they are going to show them how they treat the Jews, and they're going to show how they treat the Jews and everything.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, by the way, we are going to show where they are laying the cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "During that time-- before the [INAUDIBLE] the cemetery is quite large, the cemetery in the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many acres.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot tell you the size, but many acres.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were several shots fired during the time that the Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In about two hours these cars left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they left, they were not packed anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
